nodemanager.files

Class VersionLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • nodemanager.files.AbstractWayfindingFileHelper
      • nodemanager.files.VersionLog

  • public class VersionLog
extends AbstractWayfindingFileHelper
    Used to interact with the versions.csv file in the google drive. Since Wayfinding works by querying a manifest, we run into a problem when we create a new manifest: We need a way to keep track of previous versions, so if something goes wrong, we can just revert the update, but we also need to be able to push changes from this manager to Wayfinding without manually changing which manifest it queries. Versions.csv contains a list of manifests, which the program queries, and will run through the manifests listed until it finds one that works. Note that the VersionLog must be saved for changes to take effect. (more on this later)
